title: 'More and more' young people in ICU and dying from coronavirus: WHO
description: The World Health Organisation warns young people not to be complacent about the risk of COVID-19, noting that people in their 30s, 40s and 50s are severely ill from the virus.
content:
Posted 
April 04, 2020 14:55:24
Younger people are experiencing severe illness and dying from COVID-19, despite perceptions that the disease is only a threat to the elderly, the World Health Organisation has warned.
